'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2862] on 11 October 2000 at 3:51:42 pm'!"Change Set:		MenuDrag-arDate:			11 October 2000Author:			Andreas RaabMakes a pop-up menu reaquire the mouse focus when dropped at a new location."!!MenuMorph methodsFor: 'dropping/grabbing' stamp: 'ar 10/11/2000 14:23'!justDroppedInto: aMorph event: evt	| halo |	super justDroppedInto: aMorph event: evt.	halo _ evt hand halo.	(halo notNil and:[halo target hasOwner: self]) ifTrue:[		"Grabbed single menu item"		self addHalo: evt.	].	stayUp ifFalse:[evt hand newMouseFocus: self].! !